  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Consent of participants' primary health care physicians to participate in the aerobic
             exercise.

          -  Patients must not have participated in any consistent exercise program or
             experimental study for at least 3 months prior to enrollment.

          -  They must be capable of providing informed consent and complying with the trial
             procedures.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Demented as defined by the Modified Mini Mental Status Exam.

          -  Unalterable travel schedules.

          -  Site accessibility constraints.
      </textblock>
